      <title>在特朗普的关税揭露之前，黄金在记录下保持低于记录</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/gold-holds-ground-below-record-ahead-of-trump-s-tariff-reveal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[当市场从美国总统唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）实施批准“倒数”关税之前的创纪录的比赛中休息时，黄金稳定了，预计将在周三晚些时候生效。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/gold-holds-ground-below-record-ahead-of-trump-s-tariff-reveal</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:15:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>顶级瑞银基金经理说，关税可能会导致垃圾债券讨价还价</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/top-ubs-fund-manager-says-tariffs-may-lead-to-junk-bond-bargains</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位亚洲垃圾债券投资者去年击败了98％的竞争对手，他说他在市场上“非常看涨”；如果其他投资者惊慌失措，就准备好讨价还价。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/top-ubs-fund-manager-says-tariffs-may-lead-to-junk-bond-bargains</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:04:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>香港认为新的OTC股票市场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/hong-kong-considers-new-otc-stock-market-for-delisted-companies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[香港正在为非处方市场制定规则，以使股票的股票赋予投资者，有可能拥有越来越多的几乎毫无价值的证券的风险，有机会弥补一些损失。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/hong-kong-considers-new-otc-stock-market-for-delisted-companies</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 02 Apr 2025 00:00:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Ecopetrol Eyes购买Carlyle的哥伦比亚资产来增强储量</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ecopetrol-eyes-buying-carlyle-s-colombia-asset-to-boost-reserves</link>
      <description><![CDATA[哥伦比亚的最高高管在接受采访时说，哥伦比亚国有的Ecopetrol SA正在考虑购买凯雷集团在全国范围内购买的石油钻机，因为它希望提高储备和产出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/ecopetrol-eyes-buying-carlyle-s-colombia-asset-to-boost-reserves</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:54:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
