    <item>
      <title>特朗普的关税计划在玫瑰花园活动之前仍处于困境</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-weighing-tariff-options-as-rose-garden-event-nears</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普（Donald Trump）总统对他的计划征收互惠关税的计划的审议归因于电线，他的团队据称仍在最终确定他计划在周三下午公布的新税款的规模和范围。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/trump-weighing-tariff-options-as-rose-garden-event-nears</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:44:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>随着电动汽车削减燃料需求，大油变成中国大天然气</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/big-oil-morphs-into-big-gas-in-china-as-evs-slash-fuel-demand</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国的能源巨头越来越多地向天然气旋转以提高产量，因为对石油速度和全球贸易紧张局势的需求增加了依赖进口的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-01/big-oil-morphs-into-big-gas-in-china-as-evs-slash-fuel-demand</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 01 Apr 2025 23:36:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
